<H4>    Libya's al-Humaydi Arrives </H4>

<F P=102> LD0204100094 Tripoli JANA in English 0838 GMT 2 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD0204100094 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tunis, al-Tayr [April] 2, JAMAHIRYAH NEWS AGENCY -- 
Major al-Khuwaylidi al-Humaydi last night arrived by land [words 
indistinct] to take part in things of the Tunisian [words 
indistinct] 6th session of the Arab Maghreb Union's Presidential 
Council due to start its proceedings today in Tunis. 
  A welcoming ceremony was held for Major al-Khuwaylidi 
al-Humaydi on his arrival to his residence where he was welcomed 
by the Tunisian Prime Minister Hamed Karoui, the Minister of the 
Interior Abdallah Kallel and the general delegate of the Great 
Jamahiryah to Tunisia. 
  Major al-Khuwaylidi al-Humaydi is accompanied by delegation 
including the secretary of the General People's Committee for 
Unity and a number of experts. 

</TEXT>

