<H3> <TI>   King Receives Message on Russian Role in Peace </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    King Receives Message on Russian Role in Peace </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   JN0304180994 Amman Jordan Television Network in Arabic 1700 
GMT 3 Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0304180994 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Jordan Television Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] His Majesty King Husayn received Igor Ivanov, deputy 
Russian foreign minister and envoy of the Russian leadership to 
the region at the Royal Hashemite Court today. The meeting was 
attended by Crown Prince Hasan. 
  The envoy conveyed a message to his majesty from Russian 
President Boris Yeltsin dealing with the role that Russia can 
play in the peace process in its capacity as one of the 
cosponsors of the peace process, as well as its role in 
realizing security, stability, and prosperity in the region. 
  His majesty King Husayn emphasized the constant Jordanian 
position on the peace process, represented in the call for 
enabling the Palestinian people to attain their rights on their 
national soil, and to realize lasting, just, and comprehensive 
peace in the region. 

</TEXT>

