<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Foreign Committee Secretary Arrives in Beijing </PHRASE></F></HT>

<F P=102>   LD2903175194 Tripoli JANA in English 1709 GMT 29 Mar 94 </F>
<F P=103> LD2903175194 </F>
<F P=104>  Tripoli JANA </F>
<F P=105>  English </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Tripoli, Al-Rabia'a [March] 29, JAMAHIRIYAH NEWS 
AGENCY -- The secretary of the General Peoples Committee for 
Foreign Liaison and International Co-operation arrived in 
Beijing yesterday on a visit to the Peoples Republic of China 
where he will have contacts and consultations on the bolstering 
of the special relations and co-operation which exist between 
the Great Jamahiriyah and the Peoples Republic of China in all 
areas. 
  The Chinese Foreign Ministry yesterday held a dinner banquet 
in honour of the secretary and his accompanying delegation which 
was attended by the heads of Arab diplomatic legations based in 
Beijing as well as the secretary and members of the Libyan Arab 
peoples bureau in Beijing. 

</TEXT>

