<F P=103> NC0504093194 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 5 Apr (MENA)--Palestinian military sources 
told MENA that 100 PLO troops left today for the Egyptian border 
town of Rafah. There the troops will prepare a camp in which 
Palestinian troops coming from various destinations will 
assemble before heading to Gaza through the Rafah crossing point. 
