<F P=102>   NC0304162394 Cairo MENA in Arabic 1550 GMT 3 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0304162394 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Asyut, 3 Apr (MENA)--The security forces in Asyut 
Governorate, Upper Egypt, arrested 11 dangerous extremists 
wanted for justice during raids today on Kawm 'Abbas, 
al-Walidiyah, al- Hamra', Nazlat 'Abdallah, and al-Arba'in in 
the city of Asyut. 
  With the extremists, the forces found letters sent to them 
