<H3> <TI>   Security, Civilian Affairs Committees Meet </TI></H3>
<HT><F P=107><PHRASE>    Security, Civilian Affairs Committees Meet </PHRASE></F></HT>
<H4>    Delegate Arrives for Civilian Committee Talks </H4>

<F P=102> NC0404204894 Cairo MENA in Arabic 2030 GMT 4 Apr 94 </F>
<F P=103> NC0404204894 </F>
<F P=104>  Cairo MENA </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] Cairo, 4 Apr (MENA)--Zuhayr Lahham, member of the 
Palestinian delegation to the peace talks, arrived in Cairo from 
Tunis this evening to take part in the talks of the Civilian 
Affairs Committee. 
  Lahham will supervise the arrangements for the transfer of 
authority over telecommunications in Gaza and Jericho. 
  The Palestinian guest was received by Palestinian Ambassador 
Sa'id Kamal. 

</TEXT>

