very quick and will require only a few days. Mr. Rabin said 
this during today's cabinet session. 
  [Tel Aviv IDF Radio in Hebrew at 1300 GMT on 4 April, in a 
report by Udi Segal on the cabinet session, adds the following: 
"Prime Minister Rabin said it will take a miracle to complete 
the negotiations by the middle of this month. Rabin said there 
