territories is shaky. The government was also told that several 
mayors in the territories who had been deposed now want to 
resume office, like newly reappointed Hebron mayor Mustafa 
al-Natshah. Police Commissioner Rafi Peled said that 90 percent 
of nationalistic motivated murders of Israelis over the last 
year were perpetrated by Gaza Strip youths. 

