  [Text] Prime Minister Yitzhaq Rabin this afternoon met 
with Viktor Posuvalyuk, head of the Russian Foreign Ministry's 
Middle East Department. The Russian official, who arrived in 
the Middle East as the special envoy of President Yeltsin, 
briefed Rabin about his meetings in Tunis and Jordan. Our 
