<H4>    Meets With King Husayn </H4>

<F P=102> JN0504203294 Amman Radio Jordan Network in Arabic 2000 GMT 5 
Apr 94 </F>

<F P=103> JN0504203294 </F>
<F P=104>  Amman Radio Jordan Network </F>
<F P=105>  Arabic </F>


<TEXT>
BFN 

  [Text] The Jordanian side, led by His Majesty King Husayn, 
and the Palestinian side, led by President Yasir 'Arafat, held a 
session of talks at the al-Hashimiyah Palace today. His 
Highness Crown Prince Hasan attended the talks. 
  During the meeting, the two sides discussed the latest 
developments in the Middle East peace process and 
Jordanian-Palestinian relations. 
  The prime minister, the Royal Court chief, and a number of 
senior Jordanian and Palestinian officials participated in the 
meeting. 
  The meeting is still in session. 

